cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and text analysis to remove identifiable information from medical records. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also a likely category as the paper discusses the importance of patient privacy and confidentiality in healthcare. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another possible category as the paper deals with sensitive information and proposes a method to protect it. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning models to recognize and eliminate identifiable information. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a machine learning-based approach to scrub patient information.
